  "detailed_description": "<strong>Krakatoa </strong>is a single player Action-Adventure/Survival Horror game. Attempt to find your son and escape Siren Head. Listen closely to get an advantage in surviving an onslaught of attacks. Photo-realistic environments integrated with 3D audio bring the experience to life. Succeed in escaping and you'll live to see another day, but you can't run forever.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1436240/extras/3ae85ebfb5aa01a30e00c294a6476700.poster.avif?t=1660314723\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1436240/extras/3ae85ebfb5aa01a30e00c294a6476700.webm?t=1660314723\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1436240/extras/3ae85ebfb5aa01a30e00c294a6476700.mp4?t=1660314723\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Looking forward to any feedback as this is my first game and I'm still learning the process.<br><br>Thanks for checking it out!",
